snippet.title: ALPHA SPHERE: Director's Cut - Where To Find "Rotten Brains" Teaser
snippet.description:
Download here:
https://smwc.me/s/27795

ALPHA SPHERE: Director's Cut is the starting entry of the "ALPHA SPHERE" series, first beginning as a 1st place entry in HLDC2019. In this version there are many more secrets spread out and an extra ending to achieve.

This "secret route" grants access to the entire village of "ALPHA SPHERE Zero: Rotten Brains" a year prior to release. It shows all the remains of the old world, ending with a crushed/broken down house with the titular relic on it.
